    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain is mechanically sound, benefiting from a recent VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain chassis integrity. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension, the car delivers precise turn-in and exceptional throttle response. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, and the gear synchronization remains sharp. This is a well-maintained specimen ready for spirited canyon carving or daily enthusiast use.",
