    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend road trips. Everything runs smoothly, it looks great, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014I\u2019d love to show you around!",
